title: What Facebook's Cryptocurrency Means: 6 Predictions
text: Facebook's cryptocurrency, which it will announce shortly, could be a powerful force for good in developing countries. Facebook will likely pay interest to its users.

title: Why this former Facebook executive keeps investing in A.I. and messaging start-ups
text: Anand Chandrasekaran once worked on Facebook Messenger. Now, he's investing in start-ups that leverage AI and messaging technologies.
